content.raw:
Hi @chabachaba, thanks for the PR, but it is missing a model and the `model.config` file seems to be copied from another model.

Please check the [How to contribute a model](http://gazebosim.org/tutorials?tut=model_contrib&cat=build_robot) tutorial to learn how to contribute your own original models. I'll decline this PR for now.
